metadata.name: PHOTOE
metadata.description: "PHOTOE" is an open edition conjured of nine Dualistic Fashion editorial Photographs created by the Bailey Twins in the unique Checks style of Jack Butcher. Each photograph on this OE is part of a broader collection of 1/1 photography projects. Collectors of this open edition will have the exclusive option to burn one PHOTOE and redeem its AI Twin, an AI image created by Tevin & Tylor Bailey by referencing the photographs on PHOTOE. There are nine photographs on PHOTOE and each one corresponds to a unique AI Twin. Each AI Twin will have its own 24-hour burn/redeem event, providing collectors with a limited window of time to acquire these unique pieces.
